{"tid":247719,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"睡覺也算加班　日法院判AEON賠付177萬日元加班費","createTime":"2017-05-18T04:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:54:08.000Z","uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8305d513cafec2119405e34cbb165f627002b1e","tid":247719,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"日本知名賣場百貨AEON，昨遭千葉法院要求須給付旗下保全員工「值班睡覺」時間的加班費，總計約47萬元台幣。<br />\n這名52歲的保全員工中村孝，自2011年至2015年5月在AEON賣場擔任保全，期間曾經有多次24小時連續值班的情況，而在值班時約有4至5小時睡眠的時間，應判定為工作加班或者休息成為爭議。<br />\n中村孝認為，在值班睡覺時，自己並未外出，且保持在隨時待命狀態，應算做工時。而千葉法院昨日判決AEON需支付該員工加班費等費用，總計177萬元日幣（約46.9萬元台幣）。（國際中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170518/1120897/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170518%2F1120897%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=960a9f04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170518/1120897/</a>"},{"pid":"96aaf174081616b55fa3e76573237886a78af3fe","tid":247719,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />T不嬲no pay"},{"pid":"39dd55f36a8955f95de37edd64c1f5ffc9025604","tid":247719,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fa321b7d0049b7c3062e49fed2b31845f949c1","tid":247719,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />T不嬲no pay</blockquote><br />\n賤種奴工"},{"pid":"5f98d75e3a3f6d32fdd782106116689e1f27d903","tid":247719,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc